{"tid":1607752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】老豆老母提提大家響應全民攝衫日","createTime":"2019-10-01T03:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:29:32.000Z","uid":296674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f29f75d6834ebf25ef5c255da2c56d9828b89bf","tid":1607752,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"我係外國留學，溫書個陣老母竟然send咗呢張相比我睇，老豆仲俾我擺上連登<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovEXT8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovEXT8J.jpg&h=62104a02&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（唔該唔好搞佢後面）<br />\n<br />\n雖然我老豆從事製衣業，要同內地廠商打交道實在少不免，但係<strong>佢話唔會再返內地公幹</strong>！<br />\n我真係對佢哋呢一對終極和理非好自豪！<br />\n我冇乜嘢可以做，麻煩大家出埋我一份力，羞辱中共<br />\n記住攝衫，小心保重身體，控制自己情緒<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 One Down, Four to Go<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"10f650b6618625ae736c060b9ee137f7150513fb","tid":1607752,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68a4aa714db80a072327ba92c3deae8de6852ac7","tid":1607752,"uid":3077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"攝衫！"},{"pid":"02e246cf7df0acc1bf422481824f13fb11fa716a","tid":1607752,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34ae172eee6eacd5938634c27a3061e1eca128e6","tid":1607752,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"10。1 全民攝衫日"},{"pid":"6e09ce620c1a7e78b7c10768d949bcf79de1d92a","tid":1607752,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"10。1 文宣煲大佢"},{"pid":"28fdef218f34642574d0246e99e6144e0f1ba516","tid":1607752,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a4aa714db80a072327ba92c3deae8de6852ac7","tid":1607752,"uid":3077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"攝衫！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10